{"tid":767094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我終於諗到一個比較省錢的買六合彩方法了！","createTime":"2018-08-04T07:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T08:00:36.000Z","uid":165782,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a73e993ce54fd48f037389a30f85b8264a4614c","tid":767094,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"我終於諗到一個比較省錢的買六合彩方法了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知實有契弟會話直程唔買咪仲省錢，不過你諗下起依家香港唔買六合彩，仲有乜野發達的希望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係如果唔克制自己，期期都買咁又會變咗沉迷賭錢，實在唔掂！<br />\n<br />\n於是，我諗到一個方法去舒緩呢個問題一一就係每日用計數機ran個數出來<br />\n-&gt; 49ran#<br />\n每日ran一個number，ran咗嗰個number就排除咗佢，如果撞number就隔日重ran<br />\n就至少需要43日買一次，又或者半年都唔洗買一次<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就既可以保持住發達的希望，又唔會沉迷賭博落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2fd4e888e1334c8c805d3eb1c87756c1dfd220","tid":767094,"uid":138219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d5669bda1e1d62c632092336586056b6ae472d","tid":767094,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"咁撚麻煩<br />\n不如直接1星期20蚊算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc7011c474ffb54a8c25236e06bfec07ee2cb4d","tid":767094,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"直程唔買咪仲省錢"},{"pid":"be26c197f555c64438f9e9159ba8486bf8352c56","tid":767094,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d5669bda1e1d62c632092336586056b6ae472d","tid":767094,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T07:45:38.